results.name: Successive differences of A000990.
comment: Original definition: A000012^(-1) * A000990, where A000012^(-1) = the pairwise difference operator and A000990 = (1, 1, 3, 5, 10, 16, 29, 45, ...).
Triangle A147767 is constructed from A147766 in every column.
formula: a(n) ~ exp(2*Pi*sqrt(n/3)) * Pi^2 / (4 * 3^(7/4) * n^(9/4)). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Aug 21 2018
